description:
The story focuses on the background of Mash Kyrielight and Romani Archaman, and the events leading up to the Seventh Singularity, Absolute Demonic Front Babylonia.

This episode aired on August 3, 2019 at Fate/Grand Order Fes. 2019: Chaldea Park. It was available for download on the Fate/Grand Order mobile app, from August 4, 2019 to August 11, 2019.

Freelance animator. Often credited under his pseudonym "24㎡".
He formerly worked at [Doga Kobo](https://anilist.co/studio/95/) and is currently working at [CloverWorks](https://anilist.co/studio/6222/CloverWorks).

[Twitter](https://twitter.com/i/user/880805780844183553)

Affiliated with [CloverWorks](https://anilist.co/studio/6222/CloverWorks). 

Freelancer originating from [Doga Kobo](https://anilist.co/studio/95/), formerly a [Gainax](https://anilist.co/studio/6/) employee. 

Married to [Akira Amemiya](https://anilist.co/staff/100956/).
_Note: Not to be confused with the [painter](https://anilist.co/staff/201512/)._
